metadata.name: Project Grasp #1
metadata.description: Everyone has a friend or acquaintance who has a lot of money and no one knows how they got it. Or perhaps you are this individual. Or perhaps your friend is the most powerful Twitter influencer, capable of pumping any NFT asset. No one knows. Project Grasp is a decentralized autonomous organization (DAO) that brings together people who [REDACTED], offering [REDACTED].
